#

Veggie Quesadilla

20 min
$5
350 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 2

Allergens:

Dairy

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianQuickHealthy

Cuisine:

Mexican

Course:

Main

Tags:

EasyMexicanComfort Food

Description

A quick and delicious quesadilla filled with colorful veggies and melted cheese, perfect for a satisfying meal!

Ingredients

  • whole wheat tortillas: 2
  • bell pepper: 1, sliced
  • onion: 1, sliced
  • spinach: 1 cup, fresh
  • shredded cheese (cheddar or mozzarella): 1 cup
  • olive oil: 1 tablespoon
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
